---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for the VDA 231-301 website.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mb-8 text-sm text-[#5a7a65]">
      🇩🇪 <a href={`${base}datenschutz/`} class="text-[#1B6B3A] hover:underline">
        Deutsche Version: Datenschutzerklärung
      </a>
    </div>

    <h1
      class="mb-8 text-balance"
      style="font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 2.25rem; color: #0d3d20; line-height: 1.15;">
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-[#0d3d20]">1. Data Controller</h2>
      <address class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#2a3a30] not-italic">
        VDA 231-301 Project Group<br />
        c/o Verband der Automobilindustrie e.V.<br />
        Behrenstraße 35<br />
        10117 Berlin<br />
        Germany<br /><br />
        E-mail: <a href="mailto:info@vda.de" class="text-[#1B6B3A] hover:underline">info@vda.de</a>
      </address>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-[#0d3d20]">2. Hosting</h2>
      <p class="mb-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-[#2a3a30]">
        This website is hosted via <strong>GitHub Pages</strong> (GitHub Inc., 88 Colin P Kelly Jr St,
        San Francisco, CA 94107, USA). When you visit this website, GitHub may automatically collect and
        store server log data, including:
      </p>
      <ul class="mb-3 list-inside list-disc space-y-1 text-base text-[#2a3a30]">
        <li>IP address of the requesting device</li>
        <li>Date and time of the request</li>
        <li>URL of the requested page</li>
        <li>HTTP status code and transferred data volume</li>
        <li>Browser type and operating system (user agent)</li>
        <li>Referring URL</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#2a3a30]">
        This data is processed by GitHub as the hosting provider. For details, please refer to
        <a
          href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-[#1B6B3A] hover:underline">
          GitHub's Privacy Statement
        </a>. The legal basis for this processing is Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR (legitimate interests in
        operating a technically functional website).
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-[#0d3d20]">3. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#2a3a30]">
        This website does not use cookies. We do not employ any analytics tools, tracking scripts,
        or third-party services that collect personal data on our behalf.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-[#0d3d20]">4. Your Rights under GDPR</h2>
      <p class="mb-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-[#2a3a30]">
        Under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) you have the following rights regarding
        any personal data processed in connection with this website:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-1 text-base text-[#2a3a30]">
        <li><strong>Right of access</strong> (Art. 15 GDPR)</li>
        <li><strong>Right to rectification</strong> (Art. 16 GDPR)</li>
        <li><strong>Right to erasure</strong> ("right to be forgotten", Art. 17 GDPR)</li>
        <li><strong>Right to restriction of processing</strong> (Art. 18 GDPR)</li>
        <li><strong>Right to data portability</strong> (Art. 20 GDPR)</li>
        <li><strong>Right to object</strong> (Art. 21 GDPR)</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-[#0d3d20]">5. Right to Lodge a Complaint</h2>
      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#2a3a30]">
        You have the right to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority. The competent
        authority for the VDA is the Berlin Commissioner for Data Protection and Freedom of
        Information (<a
          href="https://www.datenschutz-berlin.de"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-[#1B6B3A] hover:underline">
          www.datenschutz-berlin.de
        </a>).
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-lg font-semibold text-[#0d3d20]">
        6. Contact for Data Protection Enquiries
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#2a3a30]">
        For any questions regarding data protection, please contact us at
        <a href="mailto:info@vda.de" class="text-[#1B6B3A] hover:underline">info@vda.de</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
